	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />They would work (with the exeption of Low G Man), but that would be a real waste considering you can find lots of cheap TLROM games arround. You'd want to preserve a TSROM or TKROM boards for a project that actually needs SRAM (like Final Fantasy 3 or the incoming Sonic game by Tokumaru)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
